values:
Boss emailed me today. I haven't opened it yet, but I figure it's nothing too bad. Last week he assigned me to a quick job- to off someone a little bit too far in debt. It was pretty simple, and there were no witnesses to make it messy.

 Also my new whore, Toshiya is bringing in a nice profit. He's a spoiled little fucker, but so long as the cash comes in I'll deal with it. He's in my bed at the moment,a nd I have this creeping feeling that he'll wake up any minute, so I'm off.

Well I've employed a new prostitute, a punk wakachu surprisingly. He came in demanding work and I more or less gave it to him. I suppose this might bring trouble sooner or later, but for now I'll keep things as they are. Toshiya is quite a valuable asset, and with him being the only male in the brothel, he'll have more than enough customers to pay for his stay.
Test. Let's see if this works.
